{
  "stem": "19550.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Who, of course, made their usual disclaimer that they didn't know anything about it, and were very offended that they were being saddled with this unexpected guest.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And subsequently a little while later, a day later-- again, the time is one mass-- I was taken to what used to be an SS hospital and sanatorium in Tutzing, in the city itself, or in the village itself.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Well, by that time, the wounded SS or the recovering SS soldiers were sort of pushed out from the facilities-- well, the better part of the facilities.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And the bullet was removed by an SS officer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "It wasn't a deep wound.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was very superficial.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "Under the very close supervision of a couple of fellow prisoners, or former prisoners, who were standing near the operating table, ready to kill the SS doctor if something happened to me.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And then I was there for a couple of days, dressed in the pajamas that these friends rustled up in the home of those two women.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And when I felt strong enough, I picked myself up and walked in those pajamas towards Feldafing, which wasn't too far from there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Which was, by that time, known as being what eventually, we called it a DP camp, where Jews began to be collected by the American soldiers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And there, I became a member of the committee of seven that organized the DP camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And and for all intents and purposes, ran it for the American military government.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And worked in the American military government office as part of my duties, as a member of the committee.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And of course, I volunteered my services to the Americans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Correct.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was more than that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the man had four years of concentration camp existence by then.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
